OL,3,CHigher Jersey bus fares blamed on
OL,4,C'significant cost increases'
OL,6,FSingle adult bus fares in Jersey have
OL,7,Frisen by 20p for contactless
OL,8,Fcustomers, marking an almost 40% price
OL,9,Fhike across the last four years.
OL,11,FAdult passengers paying by card will
OL,12,Fnow face a standard rate of #2.75,
OL,13,Fwith a contactless child ticket
OL,14,Fincreasing by 13p to #1.40.
OL,16,FAvanchiPAYG adult and child cards will
OL,17,Fsee the same uplift, to #2.45 and
OL,18,F#1.40 respectively for a single fare.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
