OL,3,CHigher Jersey bus fares blamed on
OL,4,C'significant cost increases'
OL,6,FThe cash fares are being frozen at #3
OL,7,Ffor adults and #1.50 for children,
OL,8,Fwhile those aged under five are still
OL,9,Fable to use the buses for free with a
OL,10,Fpaying grown-up.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, monthly unlimited passes
OL,13,Fwill go up by #7, with the annual
OL,14,Ftravel card now costing #550 - a #30
OL,15,Fincrease.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
