OL,3,CHigher Jersey bus fares blamed on
OL,4,C'significant cost increases'
OL,6,FIn a statement, Liberty Bus says:
OL,7,F"Since the last fare increase in 2025,
OL,8,Fbusinesses across the island, along
OL,9,Fwith ourselves, have seen significant
OL,10,Fincreases in operational costs, such
OL,11,Fas vehicle parts, labour and
OL,12,Ftechnology.
OL,14,F" In 2025, we saw 18% fewer visitors
OL,15,Fto the island, which does impact us
OL,16,Fsignificantly. Jersey is a unique
OL,17,Fplace to operate buses and the summer
OL,18,Fpassenger levels and revenue help
OL,19,Fsubsidise the winter bus service."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
