OL,3,CHigher Jersey bus fares blamed on
OL,4,C'significant cost increases'
OL,6,FIt is also running under a new service
OL,7,Fagreement, which started last year.
OL,9,FFollowing a successful tender bid, the
OL,10,Fcompany signed a 10-year contract with
OL,11,Fthe Government of Jersey to provide
OL,12,Fthe island's bus services until April
OL,13,F2035 - stating that its subsidy has
OL,14,Fbeen reduced by more than #700,000.
OL,16,FAs part of the agreement, the firm
OL,17,Fcommitted to replacing older vehicles
OL,18,Fwith 22 ultra-low emission ones -
OL,19,Fwhich it says has cost #4.8 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772568684
OL,3,CHigher Jersey bus fares blamed on
OL,4,C'significant cost increases'
OL,6,FThis, the company adds, is alongside
OL,7,F#1.275 million of investment in its
OL,8,Fageing fleet and two additional
OL,9,Felectric vehicles in December 2023.
OL,11,FA Liberty Bus spokesperson explains:
OL,12,F"Whilst we aim to keep ticket prices
OL,13,Fas low as possible, we have to make
OL,14,Fsure we are a sustainable business."
OL,16,FThe cost to replace a pass will go up
OL,17,Fto #7, while transfer tickets will
OL,18,Fremain the same price as a single fare.
OL,20,FSingle fare rises for adult
OL,21,Fcontactless customers:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
